<div>POCO C85x 5G</div></a></div></div> </div> </div> <div class="section-block section-html section-preset--bgc-3 sect_region"> <div class="section-block__header"> <h2 class="section-block__title">Latest HyperOS & MIUI Version</h2> </div> <div class="section-html__body"> <p>Other than the Chinese and global versions, Xiaomi manufactures HyperOS and MIUI for other regions. As soon as a developer creates versions for other countries, they immediately appear on our website.</p> <div class="flag_region"> <div><a href="updates/global"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/flags/mi.svg" alt="Global"><br/>Global</a></div> <div><a href="updates/china"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/flags/cn.svg" alt="China"><br/>China</a></div> <div><a href="updates/india"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/flags/in.svg" alt="India"><br/>India</a></div> <div><a href="updates/indonesia"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/flags/id.svg" alt="Indonesia"><br/>Indonesia</a></div> <div><a href="updates/europe"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/flags/eu.svg" alt="Europe"><br/>Europe</a></div> <div><a href="updates/taiwan"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/flags/tw.svg" alt="Taiwan"><br/>Taiwan</a></div> <div><a href="updates/russian"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/flags/ru.svg" alt="Russia"><br/>Russia</a></div> <div><a href="updates/turkey"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/flags/tr.svg" alt="Turkey"><br/>Turkey</a></div> <div><a href="updates/japan"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/flags/jp.svg" alt="Japan"><br/>Japan</a></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="section-block section-html section-preset--none new_arts"> <div class="section-html__body"> <div class="new"><div><a href="https://miuirom.org/updates/android-17"><picture class="attachment- size- wp-post-image" decoding="async">
